text: Jean-Luc Préel (30 October 1940 - 3 September 2015) was a member of the National Assembly of France. He represented the Vendée department, and was a member of the New Centre. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2015 deaths Category:The Centrists politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
